'''''Animals of the Bible''''' is a book illustrated by [[Dorothy P. Lathrop]] with text compiled by Helen Dean Fish.  Released by [[J. B. Lippincott Company]], it was the first recipient of the [[Caldecott Medal]] for [[illustration]] in 1938.<ref name=ALA>American Library Association: [http://www.ala.org/ala/mgrps/divs/alsc/awardsgrants/bookmedia/caldecottmedal/caldecottwinners/caldecottmedal.cfm Caldecott Medal Winners, 1938 - Present].  URL accessed 27 May 2009.</ref>

